OL,6,FMr Zahawi was made chancellor in July
OL,7,F2022 by Mr Johnson in the wake of and
OL,8,Fdozens of other ministers quitting his
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FTwo days later Mr Zahawi publicly
OL,12,Fcalled for Mr Johnson to stand down,
OL,13,Fhaving privately told him "the herd
OL,14,Fwas stampeding" and unless he resigned
OL,15,F"they are going to drag your carcass
OL,16,Fout of this place".
OL,18,FBut Mr Zahawi told the Sunday Times:
OL,19,F"I wish we had held our nerve.
